    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a super reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? This car has been my trusty companion and is in really solid shape, just waiting for its next big adventure! It runs like a dream and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to hit the pavement today, you've found it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example featuring a longitudinal 3.0L inline-six powerplant equipped with sequential multi-port fuel injection. This chassis remains remarkably composed, benefitting from a recently refreshed multilink rear suspension and upgraded monotube dampers for improved rebound control. The drivetrain delivers linear power through a crisp short-throw shifter, while the limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque vectoring during spirited cornering. Recent maintenance includes a full cooling system overhaul\u2014addressing the water pump and thermostat housing\u2014and a valve clearance adjustment. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and patina consistent with its age, the structural rigidity and powertrain health are exceptional. This is an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking a high-performance platform that prioritizes mechanical feedback over concours-level aesthetics.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title and interior. Fully operational.",
      "price": 32000.0,
