    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking both reliability and a premium driving experience. Meticulously cared for, the exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seating remains supple and supportive, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves it has never missed a scheduled maintenance interval. It shifts smoothly, brakes confidently, and sits on a set of high-quality tires with ample tread remaining. This is a complete, turn-key car that has been loved by its previous owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
