    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a brand-new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for zipping around town or hitting the open road. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go. I\u2019m honestly going to miss it, but I\u2019m excited for the next person to get behind the wheel. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
