    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a surgical throttle response and a linear climb to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, maintaining factory-spec geometry for telepathic handling. While the finish shows light patina from spirited use, the structural integrity and drivetrain synchronization are exceptional. This is a mechanically sorted example optimized for peak lateral acceleration and longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
